Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.92,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.26,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,妳还没引出贵石原有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.66,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去的话会死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:46.99,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.13,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,那 要不要试看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.07,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,命
